{"id":2297,"date":"2019-09-06T03:02:44","date_gmt":"2019-09-06T03:02:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=2297"},"modified":"2019-12-19T20:27:29","modified_gmt":"2019-12-19T13:27:29","slug":"nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#Nhung_nguyen_tac_va_dieu_kien_ve_viec_thiet_ke_Logo\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo\">Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#1_Logo_co_gia_tri_khi_the_hien_duoc_dac_diem_san_pham_dich_vu_cong_ty\" title=\"1. Logo c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb khi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, c\u00f4ng ty\">1. Logo c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb khi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, c\u00f4ng ty<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#2_Logo_khong_duoc_giong_hoac_trung_lap\" title=\"2. Logo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c tr\u00f9ng l\u1eb7p\">2. Logo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c tr\u00f9ng l\u1eb7p<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#3_Tinh_tham_my_cua_logo\" title=\"3. T\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a logo\">3. T\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a logo<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#Cac_mau_thiet_ke_logo_2019\" title=\"C\u00e1c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo 2019\">C\u00e1c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo 2019<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#1_Logo_cang_don_gian_khach_hang_cang_nho_lau\" title=\"1. Logo c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00e0ng nh\u1edb l\u00e2u\">1. Logo c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00e0ng nh\u1edb l\u00e2u<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#2_Logo_hinh_khoi_tao_su_doc_dao\" title=\"2. Logo h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o\">2. Logo h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#3_Thiet_ke_logo_co_mau_sac_ruc_ro\" title=\"3. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1\">3. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nguyen-tac-thiet-ke-logo.html\/#4_Cac_mau_logo_chu_cai\" title=\"4. C\u00e1c m\u1eabu logo ch\u1eef c\u00e1i\">4. C\u00e1c m\u1eabu logo ch\u1eef c\u00e1i<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t t\u00ean c\u00f4ng ty, c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng, qu\u00e1n \u0103n\u2026 C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 ra.<\/p>\n<p>Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ed1i b\u1eddi v\u00e0 h\u01a1i m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00ec th\u1ebf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n <strong>c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft. <\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo, <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/\">\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a> s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_nguyen_tac_va_dieu_kien_ve_viec_thiet_ke_Logo\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\">Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Logo_co_gia_tri_khi_the_hien_duoc_dac_diem_san_pham_dich_vu_cong_ty\"><\/span><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>1. Logo c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb khi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, c\u00f4ng ty<\/strong><\/span><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong <strong>c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/strong> l\u00e0 Logo ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, c\u00f4ng ty.<\/p>\n<p>S\u1ebd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu logo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a m\u00e0 khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o s\u1ebd nh\u1edb ngay \u0111\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2298\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2298\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2298\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Logo-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-t\u01b0\u1edfng-ch\u1eebng-\u0111\u01a1n-gi\u1ea3n-nh\u01b0ng-c\u00f3-nhi\u1ec1u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-c\u1ea7n-l\u01b0u-\u00fd.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\" width=\"800\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Logo-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-t\u01b0\u1edfng-ch\u1eebng-\u0111\u01a1n-gi\u1ea3n-nh\u01b0ng-c\u00f3-nhi\u1ec1u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-c\u1ea7n-l\u01b0u-\u00fd.jpg 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Logo-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-t\u01b0\u1edfng-ch\u1eebng-\u0111\u01a1n-gi\u1ea3n-nh\u01b0ng-c\u00f3-nhi\u1ec1u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-c\u1ea7n-l\u01b0u-\u00fd-300x180.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2298\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Logo thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Logo_khong_duoc_giong_hoac_trung_lap\"><\/span><em>2. Logo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ed1ng ho\u1eb7c tr\u00f9ng l\u1eb7p<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><strong>Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/strong> th\u1ee9 hai m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tr\u00f9ng l\u1eb7p. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, v\u00ec c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n cho logo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 kh\u00f3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1edfi v\u00ec sau khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, logo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd b\u1ea3o h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Do v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u01b0\u1edbc tra c\u1ee9u logo.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Tinh_tham_my_cua_logo\"><\/span><em>3. T\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a logo<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o con m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t logo, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho l\u00e0 x\u1ea5u. Cho n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3.<\/p>\n<p>Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, kh\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a logo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf font ch\u1eef, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc\u2026 M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p sao h\u00e0i h\u00f2a nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 <strong>c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo<\/strong>, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"content_sv\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_mau_thiet_ke_logo_2019\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong>C\u00e1c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo 2019<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u1ee5c n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec, h\u00e3y d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 nh\u00ecn ng\u1eafm m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 xung quanh, c\u00e1c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch, bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o v\u00e0 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n<p>L\u01b0u \u00fd: Ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 tham kh\u1ea3o, tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng sao ch\u00e9p, \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u00e1i v\u00ec n\u1ebfu vi ph\u1ea1m b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u1edfi c\u01a1 quan ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Logo_cang_don_gian_khach_hang_cang_nho_lau\"><\/span><em>1<span style=\"font-size: 100%;\">. Logo c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00e0ng nh\u1edb l\u00e2u<\/span><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty l\u1edbn tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ho\u1eb7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo theo h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eebng n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng logo ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, h\u00e3y t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi nh\u1edb th\u1eadt l\u00e2u th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1120\" src=\"https:\/\/logoaz.cdn.vccloud.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-nike.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/logoaz.cdn.vccloud.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-nike.jpg 910w, https:\/\/logoaz.cdn.vccloud.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-nike-768x198.jpg 768w\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo\" width=\"720\" height=\"186\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Logo_hinh_khoi_tao_su_doc_dao\"><\/span><em>2. Logo h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00e1c logo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo d\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. V\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ty, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh logo n\u00e0y khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf. M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n. V\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4 khan nh\u01b0ng qua tay c\u00e1c design t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ra nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu logo \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1121\" src=\"https:\/\/dichvuthuonghieu.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-hinh-khoi.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/logoaz.cdn.vccloud.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-hinh-khoi.jpg 894w, https:\/\/logoaz.cdn.vccloud.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-hinh-khoi-768x389.jpg 768w\" alt=\"thiet-ke-logo-hinh-khoi\" width=\"720\" height=\"365\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Thiet_ke_logo_co_mau_sac_ruc_ro\"><\/span><em>3. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Logo c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5. Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c m\u00e0u s\u1eafc r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u00f3c th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cao \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft n\u00ean ph\u1ed1i, s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch b\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1122\" src=\"https:\/\/dichvuthuonghieu.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-co-mau-sac-ruc-ro.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/logoaz.cdn.vccloud.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-co-mau-sac-ruc-ro.jpg 836w, https:\/\/logoaz.cdn.vccloud.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/thiet-ke-logo-co-mau-sac-ruc-ro-768x160.jpg 768w\" alt=\"thiet-ke-logo\" width=\"720\" height=\"150\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Cac_mau_logo_chu_cai\"><\/span><em>4. C\u00e1c m\u1eabu logo ch\u1eef c\u00e1i<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>D\u00f9 c\u00f3 h\u01a1i truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c logo d\u1ea1ng ch\u1eef v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Do v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea1 khi m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo n\u00e0y v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong xu h\u01b0\u1edbng 2018.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec3m l\u00e0m n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho c\u00e1c m\u1eabu logo n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 font ch\u1eef. Do \u0111\u00f3, thay v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c font ch\u1eef c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ebd, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda theo c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><em>C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-logo.html\/\">d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam g\u1ee3i \u00fd khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cho m\u00ecnh<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t t\u00ean c\u00f4ng ty, c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng, qu\u00e1n \u0103n\u2026 C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 ra. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ed1i b\u1eddi v\u00e0 h\u01a1i m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5u&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2369,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[52],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>C\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Logo hay nh\u1ea5t 2020 | \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"C\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n qua \u1ea5n ph\u1ea9m logo chuy\u00ean nghi\u